# Energy

Gives a real time current month's usage of Gas and Electricity and Smart Energy Services and Product. Also gives an estimate of the next billing cycle's usage.
This was published used the CLI Apiary command apiary publish --api-name=tolysenergy --path="/home/oracle/Apiary/cli_tolysenergy.apib"
