## Usage [/usage/current/month/{accountNumber}]

### Current Month [GET]
Returns current month's Electricity & Gas usage information on real time for the provided customer id.

+ Parameters
    + accountNumber: 4859634 (number) - Customer's account number.
    
+ Request

    + Headers
    
            tenant-id: 1 (number) - Customer's tenant-id
            api-key: 770d80e6-f580-4ae8-bea7-31d4cda37626 (number) 

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        
        {
            "account_number": "4859634",
            "name": "George",
            "gas_usage": "10,006 Btu",
            "gas_cost": "$ 36,896",
            "electricity_usage": "2,430 kW",
            "electricity_cost": "$ 22,932",
            "environment": "Canada Alberta",
            "serviceID": "8888"
        }

## Estimate [/estimate/{accountNumber}]

### Estimate [GET]
Returns an estimate of next month's usage information for the provided customer account number.

+ Parameters
    + accountNumber: 4859634 (number) - Customer's account number.

+ Request

    + Headers
    
            tenant-id: 1 (number) - Customer's tenant-id
            api-key: b1fc5825-b310-4e84-aaec-9c88c73bc81f (number) 

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "account_number": "4859634",
            "name": "Toly",
            "gas_estimate_usage": "22,000 Btu",
            "gas_estimate_cost": "$ 36,896",
            "electricity_estimate_usage": "2,430 kW",
            "electricity_estimate_cost": "$ 22,932",
            "environment": "Canada Alberta",
            "serviceID": "7777"
        }
